title: Austin INFJ INTJ INFP INTP Meetup
description: This is a friendly social space for introverts to interact and express ourselves.Find out your personality type here:https://www.truity.com/test/type-finder-personality-test-new, orhttp://www.humanmetrics.com/cgi-win/jtypes2.asp#questionnaire or, orhttps://www.16personalities.com/I am hoping to meet like-minded individuals who are introvert and intuitive (INFJ, INTJ, INFP, INTP) so we can discuss social and emotional challenges for introverts, and hopefully provide support to each other. The meetup will be casual events such as meetings at coffee shop, tea, restaurants.Helpful resources about personalities:Big 5 Test: http://www.personal.psu.edu/~j5j/IPIP/

title: Fun Austin Introverts Who Wanna Be More Extroverted!
description: We may be shy, quiet, introverted, etc WHATEVER. Let's get together and help each other break out of our shells a bit and have some fun! We'll do all sorts of fun activities around the city while sharing some drinks(if you want!) and laughs(mandatory! :) )! Let's get out there and DO THIS!Hoping for some help as well to keep the group extra fun, so if you want to be an assistant/post an occasional event, just let me know!

title: Game Night with New Friends
description: This meetup is for those looking to meet new friends in Austin and leave the comfort of home for a little bit. We will be hosting stress-free and casual game nights at Mangia Pizza every month to get to see new faces and friends every 2nd Saturday of the month. We reserve a big room to accommodate everyone for a safe and inviting environment for introverts and extroverts alike. Once in a while we may have other spontaneous events. Please come and have fun. Don't be shy! You'll be surprised who you meet with. In this meetup you will have new experiences and perspectives with the diversity Austin offers. You can meet professors, blacksmiths, singers, food critics, etc. And it is always interesting to see how others think while we talk and game. (Yes, we're looking at you Dixit and Scrabble players)

title: (Introverted) IT Professionals Moving into Leadership (AUS)
description: This online meetup is a place for Individual Contributing IT Professionals, Introverted or not, to come together with others to network and to be supported in developing practical leadership skills.

title: Introvert Internationals
description: This is a social group for those who are foreign-born and introverts. We like to do things but without being around people who are loud, and other traits usually associated with extroverts. Activities include eating out, movies, discussions about everything under the sun, arts events, and more. We are open to all activities, as long as introverts who identify with more than one culture can hang out.
